            </div>

            <div class="review-right">
                <div class="review-snippet" id="reviewSnippet">
                    <div class="review-text">"Tried to find 690 x 240 tiles to match old broken ones, and Tiles4Less were very helpful on the phone, locating the right tiles. That was on a Thursday, and the tiles arrived early Monday morning."</div>
